 <c><see cref="M:Android.Widget.AbsListView.IMultiChoiceModeListener.OnItemCheckedStateChanged(Android.Views.ActionMode, System.Int32, System.Int32, System.Int32)" /></c> events when the user
 selects and deselects list items.
